Privacy Policy
At TrendsSight Survey, operated by Arrianah Investments Ltd, we are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and disclose your personal information when you use our application ("the App").
•	Information We Collect: We collect the following information when you use the App:
o	Phone number: for account management, communication, and payment facilitation.
o	Full name: for personalization, fraud prevention, and data management.
o	Device ID: for advertisement purposes.
•	Use of Information: We use the collected information for the following purposes:
o	Account management, communication, and payment facilitation.
o	Personalization of user experience.
o	Fraud prevention and data management.
o	Advertisement targeting.
•	Data Sharing: We do not share your personal information with any third party.
•	Survey Participation: Users are encouraged to answer survey questions on social and cultural trends. All responses are valid, and users are not limited in their choices.
•	Payment: Users earn points by answering survey questions, which are converted to cash at the end of each month. Payment will be made through the user's preferred method, with communication conducted via the provided phone number.
•	Advertisements: The App may contain ads from external sources.
•	Data Security: We take reasonable measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction.
•	Updates to Privacy Policy: We reserve the right to update or modify this Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes will be effective immediately upon posting on the App.
Contact Us: If you have any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us at axisgraphics1@gmail.com.
By using the App, you consent to the collection and use of your personal information as outlined in this Privacy Policy.
